dataIdInfo.idPurp: This shapefile represents the current stock boundary for the Kohala resident stock of melon-headed whales in the main Hawaiian Islands.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This shapefile represents the current stock boundary for the Kohala resident stock of melon-headed whales in the main Hawaiian Islands. This boundary is based on biological data that have suggested a demographically-independent population of melon-headed whales is resident to this area. More information on this boundary and melon-headed whales around the Hawaiian Islands can be found in the latest stock assessment report.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: This shapefile was created from archived point data by Amanda Bradford <amanda.bradford@noaa.gov> at the NOAA Fisheries Pacific Islands Fisheries Science Center. The current projection is WGS_1984_UTM_Zone_4N.
